<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>500 Internal Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff6347;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        a {
            color: #0074b8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>500 - Internal Server Error</h1>
        <p>We're sorry, but something went wrong on our server. Our team has been notified, and we're working to fix the issue. In the meantime, you might want to return to the <a href="/">homepage</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
